{
  "name": "reactions_list-for-team-discussion-comment",
  "description": "List the reactions to a [team discussion comment](https://docs.github.com/enterprise-server@2.20/rest/reference/teams#discussion-comments). OAuth access tokens require the `read:discussion` [scope](https://docs.github.com/enterprise-server@2.20/apps/building-oauth-apps/understanding-scopes-for-oauth-apps/).",
  "parameters": {
    "type": "object",
    "properties": {
      "accept": {
        "default": "application/vnd.github.squirrel-girl-preview+json",
        "type": "string",
        "description": "This API is under preview and subject to change."
      },
      "team_id": {
        "type": "integer"
      },
      "discussion_number": {
        "type": "integer"
      },
      "comment_number": {
        "type": "integer"
      },
      "content": {
        "enum": [
          "+1",
          "-1",
          "laugh",
          "confused",
          "heart",
          "hooray",
          "rocket",
          "eyes"
        ],
        "type": "string",
        "description": "Returns a single [reaction type](https://docs.github.com/enterprise-server@2.20/rest/reference/reactions#reaction-types). Omit this parameter to list all reactions to a team discussion comment."
      },
      "per_page": {
        "default": 30,
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "Results per page (max 100)"
      },
      "page": {
        "default": 1,
        "type": "integer",
        "description": "Page number of the results to fetch."
      }
    },
    "required": [
      "accept",
      "team_id",
      "discussion_number",
      "comment_number"
    ]
  },
  "handler": "http",
  "request": {
    "method": "GET",
    "url": {
      "$uri": "http://HOSTNAME/api/v3/teams/{team_id}/discussions/{discussion_number}/comments/{comment_number}/reactions{?content,per_page,page}"
    },
    "headers": {
      "accept": {
        "$": "accept"
      }
    }
  },
  "responses": {
    "200": {
      "$encode": "markdown",
      "$block": [
        {
          "$h1": "Reaction list"
        },
        "Reactions to conversations provide a way to help people express their feelings more simply and effectively.",
        "**Key properties:**",
        {
          "$ul": [
            "**content**: The reaction to use",
            "**created_at**",
            "**id**",
            "**node_id**",
            [
              "**user**: Simple User",
              {
                "$ul": [
                  "**avatar_url**",
                  "**email**",
                  "**events_url**",
                  "**followers_url**",
                  "**following_url**",
                  "**gists_url**",
                  "**gravatar_id**",
                  "**html_url**",
                  "**id**",
                  "**login**",
                  "**name**",
                  "**node_id**",
                  "**organizations_url**",
                  "**received_events_url**",
                  "**repos_url**",
                  "**site_admin**",
                  "**starred_at**",
                  "**starred_url**",
                  "**subscriptions_url**",
                  "**type**",
                  "**url**"
                ]
              }
            ]
          ]
        },
        {
          "$each": "$.body.*",
          "$as": "item",
          "$block": [
            {
              "$h2": "Item"
            },
            {
              "$lang": "json",
              "$code": {
                "$encode": "json",
                "$indent": true,
                "$content": {
                  "$": "$.item"
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  }
}
